OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,FA warning this story contains details
OL,7,Fof a number of alleged racist
OL,8,Fincidents, which some readers may find
OL,9,Fupsetting.
OL,11,FA woman from South Birmingham says
OL,12,Fshe's endured six years of racist
OL,13,Fattacks, which have left her terrified
OL,14,Fin her own house and unable to sleep
OL,15,Fat night.
OL,17,FIn the most recent incident, 62 year
OL,18,Fold Eve says she had her windows
OL,19,Fsmashed by two men and racists slurs
OL,20,Fshouted at her.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
