OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,FThe latest attack was captured on
OL,7,FCCTV. She says it's left her petrified
OL,8,Fand vulnerable.
OL,10,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,11,FCentral, Eve said:
OL,13,F"I've been targeted for the last six
OL,14,Fyears. Finding it extremely difficult
OL,15,Fto get any form of help. I feel
OL,16,Fextremely failed by police, and by the
OL,17,Fhousing. There doesn't seem to be much
OL,18,Fhelp available.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,F"I do believe it's definitely racial.
OL,7,FI tend to know who the ringleader is,
OL,8,Fbut for some reason the police aren't
OL,9,Facknowledging or accepting anything
OL,10,FI've got to say.
OL,12,F"I mean I've got evidence I've got
OL,13,Fproof of people calling me the N-word.
OL,14,FYou know I feel dismissed as if I feel
OL,15,Fdismissed like a child of some sort.
OL,17,FEve says members of West Midlands
OL,18,FPolice came to her council home in
OL,19,FSouth Birmingham, but didn't take the
OL,20,Fbricks that were used in the attack.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,FShe believes the bricks have DNA of
OL,7,Fthe men as they didn't wear gloves.
OL,9,FShe is being supported by her family
OL,10,Fand members of the public who have
OL,11,Fencouraged her to take the bricks to a
OL,12,Fpolice station.
OL,14,FCharlie Williams, a local anti-racism
OL,15,Fcampaigner in Birmingham, took the
OL,16,Fbricks to Bournville Police Station on
OL,17,FEve's behalf, as well as the CCTV.
OL,19,FMr Williams said: "We've literally
OL,20,Fdone the police officers job for them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,F"We've handed in all the evidence,
OL,7,Fwe've handed in photographs, video
OL,8,Fevidence and also the bricks
OL,9,Fthemselves.
OL,11,F"And hopefully they realise that this
OL,12,Fcase can not close because there's
OL,13,Fsome clear evidence here."
OL,15,FWest Midlands Police said: "We're
OL,16,Finvestigating an incident of racially
OL,17,Faggravated criminal damage which took
OL,18,Fplace in South Birmingham, at around
OL,19,F6.30am on 30 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,F"We have been conducting enquiries at
OL,7,Fthe location as we seek to find those
OL,8,Fresponsible. We have given advice and
OL,9,Fsupport to the victim including
OL,10,Fissuing crime prevention devices for
OL,11,Fthe property.
OL,13,F"Our enquiries continue. We would urge
OL,14,Fpeople who may have information to
OL,15,Fplease contact us on 101 quoting crime
OL,16,Freference number 20/305231/26.
OL,17,FAlternatively, call Crimestoppers
OL,18,Fanonymously on 0800 555111.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,F"Hate crime has no place in our
OL,7,Fcommunities. Acting Chief Constable
OL,8,FScott Green has made clear the force's
OL,9,Fcommitment to ensuring hate crime
OL,10,Finvestigations are reviewed by
OL,11,Fspecially trained detectives so that
OL,12,Fvictims can have confidence their
OL,13,Freports are being taken seriously.
OL,15,F"We are determined to identify those
OL,16,Fresponsible, support victims and work
OL,17,Fwith our partners to tackle offending
OL,18,Fand protect vulnerable communities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,FEve says she has asked Birmingham City
OL,7,FCouncil for alternative housing
OL,8,Fbecause she's scared to stay in the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FShe has reported this case as a hate
OL,12,Fcrime and expected to be put on
OL,13,Fcategory band A for housing, which is
OL,14,Ffor people with the most urgent or
OL,15,Fcritical need to move.
OL,17,FShe said: "It makes me feel incredibly
OL,18,Fvulnerable, incredibly vulnerable. As
OL,19,Ffar as I know they're still there,
OL,20,Fwaiting to pounce again."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council said: "We take
OL,7,Fall reports of hate crime and
OL,8,Fantisocial behaviour extremely
OL,9,Fseriously.
OL,11,F"When residents report that they have
OL,12,Fbeen the victim of hate crime, we work
OL,13,Fclosely with the West Midlands Police
OL,14,Fand are guided by their investigations
OL,15,Fto assess the circumstances and
OL,16,Fconsider what support may be available.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784274472
OL,3,CWoman says she been subjected to
OL,4,Cracist attacks for six years
OL,6,F"It is our priority to ensure all our
OL,7,Ftenants are safe and supported. Due to
OL,8,Frecent harassment, we are arranging
OL,9,Ffor her to be placed in Band B and
OL,10,Fwill notify her.
OL,12,F"We will continue to review the
OL,13,Fsituation and her band placement,
OL,14,Fdependent on the outcome of the
OL,15,Fongoing police investigation, in
OL,16,Faccordance with our housing policy.
OL,18,F"A housing officer is in contact with
OL,19,Fher to provide support and advice."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
